metadata.name: Tiny World Pup
metadata.description:
"There is no person without a world" - Anne Carson

...but there is a world without a person ૮ ・ﻌ・ა

This is an open edition from the artist of the upcoming project Tiny World. 

Pup has worked with a number of successful artists in the music industry, and has cemented herself as a prominent illustrator. This is her debut in the NFT space.
